Package: rmdpartials
Title: Partial rmarkdown documents to prettify your reports
Description: 
		This package relies on 'rmarkdown' partials, so you can generate 
		HTML, PDF, and Word documents. It provides various helper functions to 
		make certain functions easier.
Version: 0.0.2
